name: falling through hoops
description: @sianvictoriauk - falling through hoops - a visual representation of how I feel most days, jumping through hoops to achieve my goals, only to fall and lie there stagnant for a while until I drag myself back up again -  signed right bottom corner - Originally a photograph I captured as part of an art & darkroom photography course on the 13th May 2008. I never ended up using the image. But today, 29/05/21 I've recovered it from a CD and edited it in photoshop to finally be seen.
